<h2>The Simple CRM System</h2>

<p>In this system you can:</p>
<p>
    <ul>
        <li>Create, edit and delete a client (Name, Phone number and E-Mail)</li>
        <li>Create, edit and delete client's interests</li>
        <li>Put a certain status on the client's interest</li>
        <li>See history of all client's interests</li>
    </ul>
</p>